Dialogue: 5,0:03:05.42,0:03:08.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Now that you mention it, \NI think I may have heard a strange sound.
Dialogue: 5,0:03:09.32,0:03:10.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 5,0:03:10.52,0:03:12.51,Default,,0,0,0,,A sound? What kind of sound?
Dialogue: 5,0:03:12.51,0:03:15.51,Default,,0,0,0,,It sounded a bit like sand flowing.
Dialogue: 5,0:03:15.51,0:03:17.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't hear anything like that.
Dialogue: 5,0:03:18.70,0:03:20.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard it too.
Dialogue: 5,0:03:20.11,0:03:20.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{Wha?}
Dialogue: 5,0:03:21.36,0:03:22.18,Default,,0,0,0,,When?
Dialogue: 5,0:03:22.18,0:03:24.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Today when I accidentally fell into the sea.
Dialogue: 5,0:03:24.89,0:03:25.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard it then.
Dialogue: 5,0:03:31.18,0:03:32.35,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened? Are you okay?
Dialogue: 5,0:03:32.35,0:03:34.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Apparently, she can swim now.
Dialogue: 5,0:03:34.97,0:03:36.00,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 5,0:03:36.00,0:03:38.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, it wasn't hard for me to breathe at all.
Dialogue: 5,0:03:38.56,0:03:40.24,Default,,0,0,0,,You could breathe underwater?
Dialogue: 5,0:03:40.78,0:03:41.79,Default,,0,0,0,,It seemed like it.
Dialogue: 5,0:03:41.79,0:03:46.59,Default,,0,0,0,,If I recall correctly, your mother was from Shioshishio, wasn't she?
Dialogue: 5,0:03:46.59,0:03:49.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Her birth mother was, yes.
Dialogue: 5,0:03:49.92,0:03:51.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 5,0:03:51.12,0:03:53.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Does that mean something?
Dialogue: 5,0:03:53.36,0:03:56.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Not necessarily. I'm probably just overthinking things.
Dialogue: 5,0:03:56.92,0:04:01.09,Default,,0,0,0,,But if it's all right with you, I'd like to talk to your daughter again sometime.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:01.52,0:04:02.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay...
Dialogue: 5,0:04:02.89,0:04:04.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Well then, Tsumugu,
Dialogue: 5,0:04:04.76,0:04:06.10,Default,,0,0,0,,that should be enough for today.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:06.10,0:04:07.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:07.60,0:04:09.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks, Kaname.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:09.72,0:04:10.68,Default,,0,0,0,,You've been a big help.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:11.23,0:04:12.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not sure I was of any help at all.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:12.99,0:04:14.44,Default,,0,0,0,,It was plenty, I assure you.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:15.16,0:04:18.54,Default,,0,0,0,,First Hikari{-kun} came back, \Nand now you've returned as well.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:19.04,0:04:22.20,Default,,0,0,0,,It may not be long before everyone else in Shioshishio wakes up too.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:22.70,0:04:25.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Really? Does that mean we'll be able to get into Shishio soon?
Dialogue: 5,0:04:26.28,0:04:28.46,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't say for sure,
Dialogue: 5,0:04:28.99,0:04:33.98,Default,,0,0,0,,but I believe that in order to fully understand the various weather phenomena of the last few years,
Dialogue: 5,0:04:33.98,0:04:37.04,Default,,0,0,0,,we must first go to the village of Shioshishio.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:37.85,0:04:40.04,Default,,0,0,0,,To that end, we've collected quite a bit of data.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:40.54,0:04:41.67,Default,,0,0,0,,It shouldn't be long{,} now.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:42.33,0:04:43.71,Default,,0,0,0,,We look forward to it!
Dialogue: 5,0:04:43.71,0:04:48.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanna know if Dad, Manaka, and the others are safe.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:48.51,0:04:51.60,Default,,0,0,0,,It'd probably be better not to forcefully awaken those who are still asleep.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:52.09,0:04:53.85,Default,,0,0,0,,There's still a lot that we don't know.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:54.32,0:04:55.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I know that.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:59.66,0:05:01.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you okay, Kaname{-kun}?
Dialogue: 5,0:05:01.50,0:05:02.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:02.54,0:05:05.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Or rather, none of this feels quite real yet.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:05.88,0:05:08.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, a lot has changed, \Nso you're probably just in shock.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:09.24,0:05:10.38,Default,,0,0,0,,That's true.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:10.94,0:05:11.74,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 5,0:05:12.94,0:05:14.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}there are also things that {\i0}haven't{\i1} changed.
