Dialogue: 5,0:05:30.20,0:05:33.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Sayu! Miuna{-chan}'s on the phone!
Dialogue: 5,0:05:33.82,0:05:34.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 5,0:05:40.54,0:05:42.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Make yourself comfortable.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:42.01,0:05:42.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:43.63,0:05:46.03,Default,,0,0,0,,So you really are living here, Chisaki.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:46.68,0:05:48.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Didn't I say so?
Dialogue: 5,0:05:49.42,0:05:52.17,Default,,0,0,0,,When you guys came to the fishery \Ncooperative together, I was a bit surprised.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:53.13,0:05:54.66,Default,,0,0,0,,So I may have jumped to conclusions.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:55.12,0:05:55.91,Default,,0,0,0,,You dummy.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:58.00,0:05:59.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on. Make yourself at home.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:59.71,0:06:01.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Right. Thank you.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:02.28,0:06:05.28,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll have to share a room with Mihashi{-sensei}.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:05.28,0:06:06.13,Default,,0,0,0,,That's perfectly fine.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:28.02,0:06:29.84,Default,,0,0,0,,The tea will be ready in just a moment.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:32.48,0:06:33.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 5,0:06:33.96,0:06:34.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Here you go.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:37.23,0:06:39.08,Default,,0,0,0,,My pajamas should be okay for you, right?
Dialogue: 5,0:06:39.08,0:06:40.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I laid them out already.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:40.57,0:06:41.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Kaname, yours are the blue ones.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:42.88,0:06:43.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:49.64,0:06:50.52,Default,,0,0,0,,You okay?
Dialogue: 5,0:06:50.52,0:06:51.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? What do you mean?
Dialogue: 5,0:06:52.65,0:06:54.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, Mihashi{-sensei} is here too,
Dialogue: 5,0:06:54.25,0:06:56.00,Default,,0,0,0,,so I thought there might be a lot to do.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:56.00,0:06:57.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm perfectly fine.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:58.43,0:06:59.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.07,0:07:06.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Now then,
Dialogue: 5,0:07:06.28,0:07:10.03,Default,,0,0,0,,another student from Shioshishio woke up yesterday.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:10.03,0:07:12.83,Default,,0,0,0,,We heard! Isaki{-senpai}, right?
Dialogue: 5,0:07:12.83,0:07:14.49,Default,,0,0,0,,He's good-looking, isn't he?
Dialogue: 5,0:07:14.49,0:07:15.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Yup, and totally cool.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:15.87,0:07:17.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold up!
Dialogue: 5,0:07:17.37,0:07:20.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Weren't you guys {\i1}just{\i0} saying I was \N"totally cool" when I wore the happi coat?
Dialogue: 5,0:07:20.96,0:07:23.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Is Isaki{-senpai} going to join this class too?
Dialogue: 5,0:07:23.55,0:07:24.76,Default,,0,0,0,,When is he coming?
Dialogue: 5,0:07:24.76,0:07:26.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, are you guys ignoring me?!
Dialogue: 5,0:07:33.98,0:07:34.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Man...
Dialogue: 5,0:07:35.47,0:07:38.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Just when I decided I'd live alone for the rest of my life,
Dialogue: 5,0:07:38.84,0:07:41.36,Default,,0,0,0,,he goes and wakes up all of a sudden.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:41.36,0:07:42.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I know...
Dialogue: 5,0:07:43.08,0:07:44.08,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 5,0:07:44.08,0:07:46.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I know. You're happy anyway, right?
Dialogue: 5,0:07:47.40,0:07:51.11,Default,,0,0,0,,When we were younger, \NI always just admired him from afar.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:52.66,0:07:55.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Even when we were together, \Nit always felt like he was so far away.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:56.66,0:07:58.16,Default,,0,0,0,,And the closer I got to him,
Dialogue: 5,0:07:58.16,0:08:00.56,Default,,0,0,0,,the further away he felt.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:05.18,0:08:06.17,Default,,0,0,0,,What's with you?
Dialogue: 5,0:08:06.17,0:08:07.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh...
Dialogue: 5,0:08:07.63,0:08:10.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I was just thinking that you were \Nfeeling exactly like I was back then.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:11.24,0:08:14.80,Default,,0,0,0,,But now, we may be able \N{\alpha&HFF&\fscx60}.{\r}to reach them, you know.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:16.07,0:08:17.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Things have changed.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:20.16,0:08:22.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, why don't we go see Kaname{-san}?
Dialogue: 5,0:08:22.88,0:08:23.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 5,0:08:23.98,0:08:26.73,Default,,0,0,0,,After he's gotten the chance to settle down a bit, I mean.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:27.05,0:08:29.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, b-but...
Dialogue: 5,0:08:29.44,0:08:30.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Sayu!
Dialogue: 5,0:08:30.60,0:08:32.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, r-right.{}
Dialogue: 5,0:09:03.71,0:09:07.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder if things really haven't changed...
Dialogue: 5,0:09:10.30,0:09:11.23,Default,,0,0,0,,See ya.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:11.82,0:09:13.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's give it our all, Sayu.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:13.53,0:09:14.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:15.45,0:09:17.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Give what your all?
Dialogue: 5,0:09:17.15,0:09:18.20,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a secret.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:18.20,0:09:20.06,Default,,0,0,0,,That's pretty rude.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:26.72,0:09:27.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll give it my all.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:34.35,0:09:35.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Come here.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:38.92,0:09:40.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Yo, Kaname!
Dialogue: 5,0:09:40.19,0:09:41.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard you were back!
Dialogue: 5,0:09:41.76,0:09:44.52,Default,,0,0,0,,You haven't changed a bit, of course!
Dialogue: 5,0:09:44.52,0:09:46.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, could you be...
Dialogue: 5,0:09:46.51,0:09:48.49,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Can't you tell?
Dialogue: 5,0:09:48.49,0:09:51.31,Default,,0,0,0,,It's me, Sayama. From Saya Mart.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:51.31,0:09:52.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, it {\i1}is{\i0} you.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:52.70,0:09:54.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Once you get settled in, \Nlet's all catch up sometime.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:54.94,0:09:55.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, see ya later!
Dialogue: 5,0:10:16.62,0:10:18.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, uh...
Dialogue: 5,0:10:21.00,0:10:22.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess you don't recognize me...
Dialogue: 5,0:10:24.35,0:10:25.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 5,0:10:27.52,0:10:29.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Could that have been...
Dialogue: 5,0:10:29.80,0:10:30.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Kaname?
Dialogue: 5,0:10:32.24,0:10:33.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Is something wrong?
Dialogue: 5,0:10:33.63,0:10:34.62,Default,,0,0,0,,It's nothing...
Dialogue: 5,0:10:43.61,0:10:45.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Is school enjoyable?
Dialogue: 5,0:10:45.28,0:10:47.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, more or less.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:47.29,0:10:50.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I never knew you wanted to be a nurse.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:50.81,0:10:52.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I didn't give it much thought until recently.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:54.06,0:10:56.25,Default,,0,0,0,,So it happened while I was sleeping...
Dialogue: 5,0:10:56.96,0:10:58.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you do anything interesting today?
Dialogue: 5,0:10:59.74,0:11:01.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought I'd go out and take a look around...
Dialogue: 5,0:11:02.44,0:11:05.20,Default,,0,0,0,,at what has changed,{comma for dramatic emphasis} and what hasn't.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:06.11,0:11:09.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you changed, Chisaki?
Dialogue: 5,0:11:09.98,0:11:12.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I {\i1}did{\i0} age five years.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:12.19,0:11:14.03,Default,,0,0,0,,That doesn't matter.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:14.03,0:11:15.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I like older women.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:15.66,0:11:17.07,Default,,0,0,0,,What the heck?
Dialogue: 5,0:11:17.07,0:11:18.61,Default,,0,0,0,,What about you, Kaname?
Dialogue: 5,0:11:19.05,0:11:22.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I love you, Chisaki.{PV}
Dialogue: 5,0:11:22.68,0:11:23.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,350)}I have for a long time.{PV}
Dialogue: 5,0:11:25.76,0:11:28.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you changed, Kaname?
Dialogue: 5,0:11:30.81,0:11:32.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Not in the least.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:32.75,0:11:34.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I was sleeping, after all.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:34.16,0:11:35.38,Default,,0,0,0,,That's true...
Dialogue: 5,0:11:36.44,0:11:37.96,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no way I'd change.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:51.42,0:11:54.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}A few days after Kaname{-san} came back...
Dialogue: 5,0:11:55.04,0:11:56.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 5,0:11:56.15,0:11:58.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Miuna has Ena?
Dialogue: 5,0:11:58.19,0:12:00.04,Default,,0,0,0,,After close examination,
Dialogue: 5,0:12:00.04,0:12:05.07,Default,,0,0,0,,we've confirmed that she possesses an extra membrane that is approximately fifty microns thick{ on top of her normal skin}.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:05.71,0:12:08.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Although we can't say for sure just yet,
Dialogue: 5,0:12:08.00,0:12:09.95,Default,,0,0,0,,this membrane has all the characteristics of Ena.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:10.64,0:12:15.42,Default,,0,0,0,,But I thought kids with one parent from the sea and the other from land don't have Ena.{lose across generations, so they never have it for our purposes}
Dialogue: 5,0:12:15.42,0:12:16.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought so too.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:16.43,0:12:19.98,Default,,0,0,0,,This is my first time seeing a case like this one.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:19.98,0:12:22.30,Default,,0,0,0,,If possible, I'd like to examine Akira{-kun} once too.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:26.86,0:12:28.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I still can't wrap my head around it.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:28.76,0:12:30.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, quit touching me.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:30.65,0:12:32.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Still, I sure am surprised that Miuna has Ena.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:33.61,0:12:35.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Miu has Ena?
Dialogue: 5,0:12:35.61,0:12:37.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, just like I do.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:37.64,0:12:38.73,Default,,0,0,0,,She's the same as me.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:39.12,0:12:40.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Ena, Ena!
Dialogue: 5,0:12:42.24,0:12:43.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:46.68,0:12:47.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning!
Dialogue: 5,0:12:47.93,0:12:48.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:49.48,0:12:51.00,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 5,0:12:51.00,0:12:52.12,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 5,0:12:52.12,0:12:53.82,Default,,0,0,0,,You seem sort of down.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:53.82,0:12:55.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm fine.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:55.28,0:12:56.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:57.10,0:12:59.36,Default,,0,0,0,,When did you want to go see Kaname{-san}?{PV}
Dialogue: 5,0:12:59.36,0:13:00.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not going.{PV}
Dialogue: 5,0:13:00.22,0:13:00.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 5,0:13:02.06,0:13:03.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not going.
Dialogue: 5,0:13:03.85,0:13:04.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Sayu...
Dialogue: 5,0:13:12.17,0:13:14.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder where she disappeared to.
Dialogue: 5,0:13:14.67,0:13:15.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Miuna!
Dialogue: 5,0:13:16.08,0:13:17.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go home.
Dialogue: 5,0:13:17.12,0:13:19.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, but could you go ahead without me?
Dialogue: 5,0:13:20.91,0:13:21.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Man...
Dialogue: 5,0:13:22.83,0:13:24.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't get girls at all.
Dialogue: 5,0:13:24.83,0:13:26.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Seriously.
Dialogue: 5,0:13:29.34,0:13:32.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I finally decided to come back \Nto school and check things out,
Dialogue: 5,0:13:32.56,0:13:34.30,Default,,0,0,0,,but it looks like things haven't...
Dialogue: 5,0:13:34.30,0:13:35.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh!
Dialogue: 5,0:13:37.66,0:13:40.25,Default,,0,0,0,,They kept it around so it would be here when we got back.
Dialogue: 5,0:13:41.29,0:13:44.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Miuna and everyone else \Nhave been keeping it clean for us.
Dialogue: 5,0:13:44.09,0:13:45.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 5,0:13:45.20,0:13:48.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Speaking of, Miuna{-chan}'s grown up quite a bit.
Dialogue: 5,0:13:48.20,0:13:50.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Not so much on the inside, though.
Dialogue: 5,0:13:50.24,0:13:51.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Whatever you say.
Dialogue: 5,0:13:51.76,0:13:52.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm serious.
Dialogue: 5,0:13:52.97,0:13:55.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I understand where you're \Ncoming from, though.
Dialogue: 5,0:13:56.04,0:13:58.44,Default,,0,0,0,,On the outside, she does \Nlook like she's changed.
Dialogue: 5,0:13:59.40,0:14:02.97,Default,,0,0,0,,So much has changed, \Nand at the same time, so much hasn't.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:02.97,0:14:04.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Honestly, it's pretty overwhelming.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:05.29,0:14:07.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you, by chance, \Ntrying to cheer me up?
Dialogue: 5,0:14:07.23,0:14:10.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I {\i1}am{\i0} {replace}your senior{the senpai here}, since I went and woke up before you.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:10.64,0:14:12.51,Default,,0,0,0,,You've grown up too, Hikari.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:12.51,0:14:13.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 5,0:14:15.34,0:14:16.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I had tried to prepare myself...
Dialogue: 5,0:14:17.92,0:14:20.20,Default,,0,0,0,,ever since I heard we'd have to go to sleep.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:20.92,0:14:23.76,Default,,0,0,0,,But now that it's actually happened, it's harder than you thought, huh?
Dialogue: 5,0:14:24.83,0:14:26.76,Default,,0,0,0,,You really {\i1}have{\i0} changed, Hikari.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:27.40,0:14:30.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Even though you woke up \Nright before I did, you've changed a lot.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:30.75,0:14:31.69,Default,,0,0,0,,You think so?
Dialogue: 5,0:14:31.69,0:14:32.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:32.99,0:14:38.14,Default,,0,0,0,,If you could change so much in such a short time, \NI can't imagine how much has changed in five years.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:38.92,0:14:40.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:40.60,0:14:41.93,Default,,0,0,0,,You might be right.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:42.94,0:14:45.15,Default,,0,0,0,,In that case, I won't change any more.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:45.82,0:14:47.42,Default,,0,0,0,,'Cause if I do,
Dialogue: 5,0:14:47.42,0:14:50.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Manaka might get too shocked \Nonce she wakes up.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:52.46,0:14:55.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, now that you've woken up, \Nshe might soon too.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:56.06,0:15:00.54,Default,,0,0,0,,When she does, she probably won't \Nhave changed at all since back then.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:01.32,0:15:03.42,Default,,0,0,0,,She'll probably still like Tsumugu, too.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:06.99,0:15:09.55,Default,,0,0,0,,But even so, I'm not gonna change.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:09.55,0:15:10.97,Default,,0,0,0,,No matter what.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:10.97,0:15:12.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Hikari...
Dialogue: 5,0:15:41.68,0:15:42.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Sayu!
