Dialogue: 1,0:15:42.88,0:15:45.43,Naru Nami Shine,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.6\c&HC9875D&\fscx51\fscy51\pos(999,228)\frz358.9\b1}Do Not Enter
Dialogue: 2,0:15:42.88,0:15:45.43,Naru Nami Shine,,0,0,0,,{\an5\bord0\blur1\p1\fscx178\fscy13\c&HFFFFFF&\frz355.5\pos(998,231)\1a&HA7&}m 0 0 l 100 0 100 100 0 100
Dialogue: 5,0:15:45.92,0:15:48.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought it was finally possible to get a little closer...
Dialogue: 5,0:15:48.81,0:15:51.15,Default,,0,0,0,,...but we're still so far away.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:51.15,0:15:52.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Man...
Dialogue: 5,0:15:53.31,0:15:55.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess I'm on my own after all.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:55.71,0:15:59.84,Default,,0,0,0,,But you know, nothing ever comes from childhood crushes anyway.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:59.84,0:16:03.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm bound to forget these feelings one day.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:04.36,0:16:05.36,Default,,0,0,0,,You really think so?
Dialogue: 5,0:16:05.36,0:16:06.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Absolutely.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:06.97,0:16:09.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Though I may try to be tough and independent,
Dialogue: 5,0:16:09.63,0:16:12.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll probably come to like some other guy eventually.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:12.92,0:16:16.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Or maybe I'll wind up with someone I don't like, \Njust to avoid being lonely.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:17.08,0:16:18.54,Default,,0,0,0,,That's just how things are.{how it goes?}
Dialogue: 5,0:16:18.54,0:16:22.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Feeling the same way about \Nthe same person after all these years...
Dialogue: 5,0:16:22.08,0:16:23.64,Default,,0,0,0,,It's ridiculous!
Dialogue: 5,0:16:23.64,0:16:25.58,Default,,0,0,0,,That's just something \Nout of a manga or a drama.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:26.16,0:16:28.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't believe I've felt this way \Nfor five whole years.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:28.33,0:16:30.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been so self-absorbed.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:30.86,0:16:34.19,Default,,0,0,0,,It's gross and pathetic and horrible...
Dialogue: 5,0:16:34.19,0:16:35.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I must be sick!
Dialogue: 5,0:16:37.15,0:16:38.52,Default,,0,0,0,,That's...
Dialogue: 5,0:16:39.74,0:16:41.02,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not true!
Dialogue: 5,0:16:41.02,0:16:42.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, it is!
Dialogue: 5,0:16:42.06,0:16:43.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Is not!
Dialogue: 5,0:16:43.07,0:16:44.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Is too!
Dialogue: 5,0:16:44.19,0:16:45.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Is not!
Dialogue: 5,0:16:45.07,0:16:45.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Is too!
Dialogue: 5,0:16:46.92,0:16:49.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I've made up my mind. \NI'm not going to change.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:49.05,0:16:50.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 5,0:16:53.74,0:16:56.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't care if I'm sick or if I seem \Nlike some character out of a manga.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:57.18,0:16:58.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if it's gross,
Dialogue: 5,0:16:58.64,0:17:00.06,Default,,0,0,0,,even if it's pathetic,
Dialogue: 5,0:17:00.56,0:17:02.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not going to change!
Dialogue: 5,0:17:02.70,0:17:04.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I refuse to!
Dialogue: 5,0:17:13.56,0:17:15.87,Default,,0,0,0,,You refuse to change? Are you kidding?
Dialogue: 5,0:17:15.87,0:17:18.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, Miuna. You're not making any sense.
Dialogue: 5,0:17:21.97,0:17:24.46,Default,,0,0,0,,What's this? Are you on your own today too?
Dialogue: 5,0:17:25.58,0:17:26.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Come here.
Dialogue: 5,0:17:28.16,0:17:29.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess you still won't come near me—
Dialogue: 5,0:17:29.18,0:17:29.94,Alternative,,0,0,0,,Sayu{-chan}.{This 3D O.o}{wut}
Dialogue: 5,0:17:43.93,0:17:45.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-Who are you?
Dialogue: 5,0:17:45.80,0:17:47.93,Default,,0,0,0,,It's been a while, Sayu{-chan}.
Dialogue: 5,0:17:49.87,0:17:52.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, um...
Dialogue: 5,0:17:53.24,0:17:55.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-Yeah! It {\i1}has{\i0} been a while!
Dialogue: 5,0:17:55.96,0:18:00.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Then again, maybe it hasn't exactly been a while. For you, I mean—
Dialogue: 5,0:18:00.57,0:18:02.26,Default,,0,0,0,,You haven't changed.
Dialogue: 5,0:18:02.65,0:18:04.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, sorry.
Dialogue: 5,0:18:04.41,0:18:06.27,Default,,0,0,0,,We're the same age now.
Dialogue: 5,0:18:11.69,0:18:14.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm sick too.
Dialogue: 5,0:18:17.82,0:18:19.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Hikari! Hold on!
Dialogue: 5,0:18:21.66,0:18:22.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry!
Dialogue: 5,0:18:22.67,0:18:24.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, where are you going, Hikari?
Dialogue: 5,0:18:24.45,0:18:27.12,Default,,0,0,0,,There could be a way for me \Nto get into Shioshishio!
Dialogue: 5,0:18:28.76,0:18:29.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Jeez...
Dialogue: 5,0:18:30.72,0:18:34.76,Default,,0,0,0,,The key is the sound that Isaki{-kun} \Nand Shiodome{-kun} said they heard.
Dialogue: 5,0:18:35.36,0:18:38.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I believe that the sound might \Nbe caused by an unknown current.
Dialogue: 5,0:18:39.12,0:18:40.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Keeping that in mind,
Dialogue: 5,0:18:40.38,0:18:44.51,Default,,0,0,0,,we rewatched the video footage \Nfrom our underwater expeditions
Dialogue: 5,0:18:44.51,0:18:49.53,Default,,0,0,0,,and were able to pinpoint that current, \Nwhich seems weaker than those nearby.
Dialogue: 5,0:18:50.50,0:18:52.90,Default,,0,0,0,,The current originates \Nfrom somewhere around here.
Dialogue: 5,0:18:54.67,0:18:57.29,Default,,0,0,0,,It's right {around }where the village \Nof Shioshishio should be.
Dialogue: 5,0:18:57.29,0:19:01.37,Default,,0,0,0,,This current may be the first sign that \Nthe power encasing the village is failing.
Dialogue: 5,0:19:01.96,0:19:04.70,Default,,0,0,0,,So all we have to do to get to the village \Nis get through that current?
Dialogue: 5,0:19:04.70,0:19:07.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Right now, this is all just theory.
Dialogue: 5,0:19:08.28,0:19:13.09,Default,,0,0,0,,In other words, we won't know \Nfor sure until we actually try, right?
Dialogue: 5,0:19:13.09,0:19:14.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 5,0:19:14.28,0:19:17.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Which is why we wanted to \Nask you and Hikari to help us out.
Dialogue: 5,0:19:17.88,0:19:19.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course we will!
Dialogue: 5,0:19:19.23,0:19:20.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Just leave it to us!
Dialogue: 5,0:19:20.78,0:19:22.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure, I'll help, but...
Dialogue: 5,0:19:22.16,0:19:25.89,Default,,0,0,0,,you said that that sound \Nis the key to all this, right?
Dialogue: 5,0:19:23.60,0:19:25.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\an8}Hikari's going back to Shioshishio...
Dialogue: 5,0:19:25.89,0:19:30.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Right, though we don't yet \Nknow exactly what it means.
Dialogue: 5,0:19:29.07,0:19:30.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\an8}To the world he used to live in.
Dialogue: 5,0:19:30.80,0:19:33.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Kaname, you heard that sound, right?
Dialogue: 5,0:19:33.31,0:19:34.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, I'll leave it to you to lead us.
Dialogue: 5,0:19:35.32,0:19:37.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't hear it that clearly, though.
Dialogue: 5,0:19:37.56,0:19:40.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Really? What are we gonna do, then?
Dialogue: 5,0:19:40.54,0:19:42.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}To where Manaka{-san} is.
Dialogue: 5,0:19:44.92,0:19:46.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to help too!
Dialogue: 5,0:19:46.80,0:19:49.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard the sound clearly.
Dialogue: 5,0:19:49.26,0:19:51.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure I'll be able to hear it again!
Dialogue: 5,0:19:52.30,0:19:55.26,Default,,0,0,0,,You said I have Ena, didn't you?
Dialogue: 5,0:19:55.26,0:19:58.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Then I should be okay in the sea, right?
Dialogue: 5,0:19:58.26,0:20:00.17,Default,,0,0,0,,That may be true, but...
Dialogue: 5,0:19:59.28,0:20:00.17,Alternative,,0,0,0,,Miuna!
Dialogue: 5,0:20:00.62,0:20:04.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I know you want to help, \Nbut won't it be dangerous for you?
Dialogue: 5,0:20:04.33,0:20:06.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Your Ena's not really complete.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.93,0:20:09.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I know...
Dialogue: 5,0:20:09.74,0:20:10.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't we let her?
Dialogue: 5,0:20:11.76,0:20:13.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Kaname and I will be with her, after all.
Dialogue: 5,0:20:13.61,0:20:14.98,Default,,0,0,0,,There'll be nothing to worry about.
Dialogue: 5,0:20:16.08,0:20:17.23,Default,,0,0,0,,We're counting on you, Miuna.
Dialogue: 5,0:20:19.20,0:20:20.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 5,0:20:26.67,0:20:29.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you sure it's all right if I don't go?
Dialogue: 5,0:20:30.04,0:20:31.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, it's fine.
Dialogue: 5,0:20:32.84,0:20:33.67,Default,,0,0,0,,See you later.
Dialogue: 5,0:20:41.13,0:20:43.72,Default,,0,0,0,,The water temperature's pretty low.
Dialogue: 5,0:20:43.72,0:20:45.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't underestimate our Ena!
Dialogue: 5,0:20:45.58,0:20:46.88,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll be just fine.
Dialogue: 5,0:20:47.84,0:20:50.72,Default,,0,0,0,,If anything unexpected happens, come back right away.
Dialogue: 5,0:20:50.72,0:20:51.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 5,0:20:54.70,0:20:55.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Here we go!
Dialogue: 5,0:21:02.09,0:21:03.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it too cold?
Dialogue: 5,0:21:03.50,0:21:04.61,Default,,0,0,0,,It's fine.
Dialogue: 5,0:21:20.36,0:21:22.91,Default,,0,0,0,,You sure you can breathe okay?
Dialogue: 5,0:21:22.91,0:21:23.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. 
Dialogue: 5,0:21:23.86,0:21:25.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I practiced a lot before today.
Dialogue: 5,0:21:25.68,0:21:28.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Still, make sure you don't \Npush yourself, all right?
Dialogue: 5,0:21:28.65,0:21:29.56,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 5,0:21:29.56,0:21:31.20,Default,,0,0,0,,So can you hear that sound right now?
Dialogue: 5,0:21:31.93,0:21:33.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't hear anything.
Dialogue: 5,0:21:34.73,0:21:35.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Me neither.{Miuna superpowers concentration~}
Dialogue: 5,0:21:41.08,0:21:42.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I hear it.
Dialogue: 5,0:21:42.59,0:21:43.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I can hear it!
Dialogue: 5,0:21:44.32,0:21:45.29,Default,,0,0,0,,This way!
Dialogue: 5,0:21:45.77,0:21:47.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, wait up, Miuna!
Dialogue: 5,0:21:49.10,0:21:51.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}To a world completely unknown to me...
Dialogue: 5,0:21:53.34,0:21:56.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}To the mysterious world Hikari is from.
